Pixie Davies https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pixie_Davies 0 Pixie Davies is an English child actress who has starred in many notable films and TV series, including Roald Dahl's Esio Trot, The Secret of Crickley Hall, Humans, Miss Peregrine's Home for Peculiar Children, and Mary Poppins Returns.
